                "text": "Azers can cause any weapon they wield to deal half its damage as fire damage, becoming lethal and non-archaic if it is not already. If the weapon already deals two damage types, this effect replaces one with fire. In addition, azers can grant weapons they wield the burn critical hit effect (1d4, 2d4 at CR 6, 3d4 at CR 11, and 3d4 at CR 16+). If the weapon has any other critical hit effects, the azer chooses only one to apply on a critical hit.",
